description:
Nathan is a straight soccer player who is engaged to his girlfriend of five years. When I asked him if his girlfriend knew that he was doing erotic modeling, he grinned and claimed she did. Apparently, she is OK with it as long as no other women are involved (which I don't think will be a problem here!).
Nathan is kind of quiet but not at all ashamed of his beautiful, smooth body. He looks very conservative, but looks can be deceiving...
title: Nathan
